high_descs: Go forward all the way, turn right, go forward all the way to the counter with the toaster.
Take the knife on the counter from behind the plate.
Stay at the counter.
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Turn to the left.
Put the knife on the counter to the right of the tomato.
Turn to the right.
Take a slice of tomato from the counter.
Turn around, go forward, turn right to the oven.
Cook the tomato in the microwave about the oven then take it out.
Turn around, go forward, turn left at the sink, go to the sink.
Put the tomato on the right side of the sink.
